     H            Y.
     F** EDIR13 *********************************
     F* IAF ONE WAY KANBAN RE-PRINT             *
     F* BACK UP DATA => CREATE OF RE-PRINT DATA *
     F*    C:N.HAYAKAWA    1997.09.23           *
     F*    UPDATE  1997.10.10:       %0002      *
     F*                         ORDER NO ADDING *
     F*******************************************
     FEDIPW13 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FINPUT   IP  F     256            DISK
     FEDIWP11 O   F     256            DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1  12 60               ERR MESSAGE
     IINPUT   AA  05
     I                                        1 256 ALLDAT
%0002I*                                     110 1120ISEQ
%0002I                                      120 1220ISEQ
     C**********************
     C*  DISPLAY 1 SCREEN  *
     C**********************
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '0'
     C                     SETON                     50
     C           STP1      TAG
     C                     EXFMTEDIPW131
     C                     SETOF                     010299
     C*
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
     C*  CHECK OF PAGE  *
     C           @FROM     IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVE ER,1      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           @TO       IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVE ER,2      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           @FROM     IFGT @TO
     C                     SETON                     010299
     C                     MOVE ER,3      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C* CMD-5 CHECK *
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STP1
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
     C* DATA MAKING *
     C           @FROM     IFGT ISEQ
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     ENDIF
     C           @TO       IFLT ISEQ
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     EXCPTOUT
     C           END       TAG
     OEDIWP11 EADD             OUT
     O                         ALLDAT   256
**  ER
E-01 PAGE NO.ISN'T IT. INPUT IT.(TO)
E-02 PAGE NO.ISN'T IT. INPUT IT.(FROM)
E-03 STARTING PAGE IS LAGER THEN ENDING PAGE.
